      <lg xml:id="TVM1.6.9">
<l>taruma varumpaya ṉāya</l>
<l>tirumaka ḷārtaṉik kēḷvar</l>
<l>perumai yuṭaiya pirāṉā</l>
<l>rirumai viṉaikaṭi vārē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The sole husband of the lady Śrī</l>
<l>who is the rare fruit of dharma,</l>
<l>the lord who possesses greatness</l>
<l>will expell [your] twofold karma.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
